999827", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031547_1021011429333160_4176289926510597494_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=ISuE7zAlNHQQ7kNvgGX-Mzh&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCnvbEZyRDw7AWos_XV_YnlTDRIfCIJ5ZPIH40gxmyaSA&oe=66FE7EE1"}, {"file_name": "Artboard 4.png", "id": "524012790104112", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39001669_524012793437445_4891316513078544414_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=1Bd3ahGkXxoQ7kNvgHd3NKc&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYC2H78ULACx-Y2X3dIW4SGDEPeQFVZKsopINMYr9vdxzQ&oe=66FE935A"}, {"file_name": "Artboard 3.png", "id": "1187574142495669", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031470_1187574145829002_8495108821353233334_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=GUdObN1QwkQQ7kNvgGGAY9V&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDAGX6DeD1XggU9uOg-mFJzL0lSYedRU3GWMHH44GdttQ&oe=66FE85F0"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "38974450_2251639131854765_8396477208328520911_n.png", "id": "529809686395654", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75476759_529809689728987_2021663405477506286_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=QrlvX5aflBwQ7kNvgHRuYth&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYC9lR-t4B-zOU4Sg3AhoMlcji5kn_xTq7mW7se3-4O5mg&oe=66FE77FF"}, "display_name": "Cellular Safari", "keywords": [], "long_description": "**Safari Cellular** is an innovative virtual reality app that turns learning about **cellular biology** into an exciting adventure. Designed for **students, educators and science enthusiasts**, this app allows you to explore an **animal cell in 3D** like never before. Through an immersive interface, you can navigate through different cell structures, such as **the nucleus, mitochondria, and endoplasmic reticulum**, discovering their functions and importance.\n\nEach component of the cell is represented in stunning detail, allowing you to observe and understand complex biological processes in a visually engaging way. **Integrated artificial intelligence** is at your disposal to answer any questions you may have while exploring, providing clear and detailed explanations.\n\nCellular Safari is not just a passive educational experience; it includes a series of **mini interactive games** designed to consolidate your knowledge in a fun and engaging way. Through **challenges and quizzes**, you can test your understanding of biological concepts, making learning an active and stimulating process.\n\nPerfect for use in education or as a self-study tool, Cellular Safari offers a new and innovative way to explore the microscopic world of the animal cell. With **high-quality graphics** and an **intuitive user experience**, this app turns the study of biology into an unforgettable adventure.", "short_description": "Discover the fascinating world of the animal cell with Cell Safari, the educational VR app that allows you to explore cell structures in 3D. Through interactive mini-games and advanced artificial intelligence, learn scientific concepts while having fun. Ideal for students and biology enthusiasts, this immersive experience makes learning an exciting adventure."}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_name": "Landscape Mini.png", "id": "2930927027073306", "image_type": "APP_IMG_SMALL_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974477_2930927030406639_1033799740283778117_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=xbHIQDl7TsIQ7kNvgFCPSiB&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBWkQxspBIls8SC3y50kc4USjmgGR3ccsD-pSQXGmqOZg&oe=66FE718E"}, {"file_name": "Hero Cover.png", "id": "1897915367381648", "image_type": "APP_IMG_HERO", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75207242_1897915370714981_6546028005331927603_n.png?_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=X6JmICvlhC0Q7kNvgF9h_If&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYC4NUNNbVt9ZUNQuKigODRUlmWxssJiZyPgda2vL-XDkg&oe=66FEA10D"}, {"file_name": "Logo.png", "id": "1156101178831306", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982713_1156101182164639_3284781712281521597_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=az2K2SdHKugQ7kNvgEJ3OWI&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYA5_od1OAjEQvzVuez24rV-ZGu1TeQAKMNvVbRFcKb7Pw&oe=66FE6ECF"}, {"file_name": "Landscape.png", "id": "1035480321561334", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_LANDSCAPE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982526_1035480328228000_568917300582159945_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=KwbwIGFJdAAQ7kNvgG0OTQG&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCkfBzooq1yMMBZdOfh_U-9n0nTf_nPJ7I1wjpEBmQr0Q&oe=66FE9138"}, {"file_name": "Landscape Portrait.png", "id": "840716281119571", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_PORTRAIT", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/57574720_840716291119570_6338633741422904364_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=LRHJqaIhjcEQ7kNvgE-i41o&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDKd3tbT9vuIPhYj_K_zX71jIWICDZvXzBKWRl5leHwZg&oe=66FE6BDB"}, {"file_name": "Icon.png", "id": "488412717275961", "image_type": "APP_IMG_ICON", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974525_488412720609294_7458364120634917665_n.png?_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=xxOSi1uuyk0Q7kNvgF1o9V9&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDmXCw_MBEo95WI7iEcfKIMlDE8kGXE8IYwhxnj4orQnw&oe=66FE9551"}, {"file_name": "Landscape Square.png", "id": "427144199756021", "image_type": "APP_IMG_COVER_SQUARE", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75223486_427144203089354_4369279694658394896_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=YCsguHoj4v0Q7kNvgFnC8hA&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBAsljyW_xJ2TGr4Rb0YVlryZSQOeqLQx2LcXFfO2-5Vg&oe=66FE740F"}]}, "id": "520469743690183", "locale": "it_IT", "screenshots": [{"file_name": "Artboard 5.png", "id": "422140790868918", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031547_422140794202251_1640211663921085746_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=qLThEBUEebAQ7kNvgFQ-uc7&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYARl2b46Z2PAsnubatRfHX7uA-Ubq_V8aTlzfRL0pc6Ew&oe=66FE7C2A"}, {"file_name": "Artboard 2.png", "id": "468838062692515", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38984464_468838066025848_9209980070403449565_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=N9sKF7Yr2xcQ7kNvgEzI13o&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAjNyuSZ1khdXXNPnKRRshkI5Q3M592OpVXYUKbL2iuvQ&oe=66FE780C"}, {"file_name": "Artboard 4.png", "id": "481654227990009", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031353_481654234656675_3114596455803752280_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=TBB76Zm-1kQQ7kNvgFHQsTj&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAor-fs5PHRoprDnppUnIcSURGnbg68aWjxw2vq2fUtSQ&oe=66FE7690"}, {"file_name": "Artboard 3.png", "id": "3889565187981667", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031547_3889565191315000_5528783709779854295_n.png?_nc_cat=106&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=wvhkhkFP8zwQ7kNvgHABKJX&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAk9daTYjaJ7xah1_eHcRjR74ZrEWnFxWjIR2p7UzIvrQ&oe=66FE7624"}, {"file_name": "Artboard 1.png", "id": "867384681933118", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39003244_867384685266451_2340853765823917163_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=mpOFdtrwTdkQ7kNvgFUFE-e&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDHlPe_0MgP6crYzIgBCrYvziJoA8oPO9RQlfXWjtD0Nw&oe=66FE7A45"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "38974450_2251639131854765_8396477208328520911_n.png", "id": "999991165259980", "uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75476756_999991168593313_5483195490028886346_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=Arl-bTTq9VAQ7kNvgHWGZje&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBNgJ_G8lx_C4pbKmE8a3qtr04gA-fc0W7cZ2rwXuhubw&oe=66FE87B1"}, "display_name": "Safari Cellulare", "keywords": [], "long_description": "**Safari Cellulare** \u00e8 un'applicazione di realt\u00e0 virtuale innovativa che trasforma l'apprendimento della **biologia cellulare** in un'avventura emozionante. Progettata per **studenti, educatori e appassionati di scienza**, questa app ti permette di esplorare una **cellula animale in 3D** come mai prima d'ora. Attraverso un'interfaccia immersiva, puoi navigare tra le diverse strutture cellulari, come **il nucleo, i mitocondri e il reticolo endoplasmatico**, scoprendone le funzioni e l'importanza.\n\nOgni componente della cellula \u00e8 rappresentato con dettagli straordinari, permettendoti di osservare e comprendere i processi biologici complessi in modo visivamente accattivante. **L'intelligenza artificiale integrata** \u00e8 a tua disposizione per rispondere a qualsiasi domanda tu possa avere durante l'esplorazione, fornendo spiegazioni chiare e dettagliate.\n\nSafari Cellulare non \u00e8 solo un'esperienza educativa passiva; include una serie di **mini giochi interattivi** progettati per consolidare le tue conoscenze in modo divertente e coinvolgente. Attraverso **sfide e quiz**, puoi mettere alla prova la tua comprensione dei concetti biologici, rendendo l'apprendimento un processo attivo e stimolante.\n\nPerfetta per l'uso in ambito educativo o come strumento di autoapprendimento, Safari Cellulare offre un modo nuovo e innovativo per esplorare il mondo microscopico della cellula animale. Con **grafica di alta qualit\u00e0** e un'**esperienza utente intuitiva**, questa app trasforma lo studio della biologia in un'avventura indimenticabile.", "short_description": "Scopri l'affascinante mondo della cellula animale con Safari Cellulare, l'app VR educativa che ti permette di esplorare le strutture cellulari in 3D. Attraverso mini giochi interattivi e un'intelligenza artificiale avanzata, apprendi concetti scientifici divertendoti. Ideale per studenti e appassionati di biologia, questa esperienza immersiva rende l'apprendimento un'avventura entusiasmante."}, {"images": {"nodes": [{"file_na